channel.title: A bunch of my projects disappeared when I updated to 5.4
channel.description: I wanted to work on a song only to see that and many other of my projects have been missing, has this happened to anyone else

item.title: A bunch of my projects disappeared when I updated to 5.4
item.dc:creator: Auxy
item.description:
Yes! Please tap “import” and locate iCloud Drive/Auxy where you should be able to find and select any missing projects.

Also contact support if you have problems restoring any projects etc!
